title: How to Curl a Low Fade | AXE | Instagroom
description:
Watch Kel jam his low fade in a few smooth moves. Boom. Dancefloor’s calling. 

THE TOOLS:
AXE Natural Look Softening Cream
Curl sponge

THE STEPS:
1. Rub cream on hands
2. Rub through hair
3. Sponge for a nice texture

transcripts: Appearance is important to me, because if you look good you feel good. Basically I take the cream. Rub it in my hands. Rub that through my hair. Then I get the sponge, and make little circles. I’m ready to go.
